            <div class="tree-item"><span class="tree-branch">│   ├── </span><span class="tree-file">MIL-Spec Testing</span><span class="tree-leader"></span><span class="tree-context">shock, vibration, environmental</span></div>
            <div class="tree-item"><span class="tree-branch">│   └── </span><span class="tree-file">Rapid Prototyping</span><span class="tree-leader"></span><span class="tree-context">concept-to-test iteration</span></div>
